<p>Each Sunshine Day Nursery provides a professional childcare service which is registered with OFSTED.</p>
<h3>Sunshine Day Nursery @ Northern General Hospital</h3>
<p>The Northern General Hospital nursery has places for 114 children each day aged between four months and five years old. It is situated by the Rivermead Training Centre and comprises of 2 Buildings:</p>
<ul>
	<li>The Daleside Building takes children from four months to 3 years (approx) in three groups (Orange, Green and Red Room). The Management Team are also based in this building.</li>
	<li>The Rother Building takes children up to school entry age from 36 months onwards who are split into two age groups; three to four years (Blue Room) and four years to school entry (Pre-School). The Childcare Services Manager is also based in this building.</li>
</ul>
