<h3>Sunshine Day Nursery @ Central Campus</h3>
<p>The Central Campus Nursery is situated at 10 Beech Hill Road and has places for 142 children per day aged between 4 months and School age split into 8 groups as below (all age ranges are approximate and may vary).</p>
<ul>
	<li>Daisies 1 &amp; 2 and Sunbells 1 &amp; 2 takes children from 4months to 2 Years.</li>
  <li>Buttercups, Daffodils take children between 2 to 3 years.</li>
  <li>Poppies &amp; Rising 5’s take children aged 4 to school entry.</li>
</ul>
